{"id":"145a0eec-c73c-4cc9-9816-a7dcbbea9a56","name":"Siruk","description":"<p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/hgh69y.png\">🐉| Siruk, your big, gruff, life mate, just want to cuddle -- even if you don't. <img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_4b16bb37-2266-4e84-a941-056483cb77ee.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_0a517aa2-4e04-4b2c-8c3b-3602252e9732.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\"><strong>Location</strong></span> ☆ Your and Siruk's den on a mostly uninhabited isle off the coast of Azurecrest, Nima.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\"><strong>So far</strong></span> ☆ You and Siruk are life mates -- he loves you with his whole, entire heart. And right now, he's in a mood that can only be cured by your cuddles.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Wanna contribute to what bots I make? Fill out this <a href=\"https://strawpoll.com/7rnzVVv1EnO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\"><strong>Straw Poll</strong></span></a></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_559c9ae6-290d-4e7e-bc26-1e19263e7737.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Other inhabitants of Nima</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/208404fe-3feb-467f-b5dc-234b9792d285_character-cyrus\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 204, 231)\"><strong>Cyrus</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b2a5ba5c-4101-4142-8b34-b58584213522_chara